00:11:19.760 --> 00:11:20.260
maybe?

00:11:20.260 --> 00:11:23.380
PROFESSOR: How does she talk?

00:11:23.380 --> 00:11:24.050
Kind of robotic?

00:11:24.050 --> 00:11:26.300
AUDIENCE: It's robotic, but
also like a woman's voice.

00:11:26.300 --> 00:11:29.120
PROFESSOR: There's a
