00:11:36.310 --> 00:11:38.420
Why a triangle and not a square?

00:11:38.420 --> 00:11:39.912
Or circle?

00:11:39.912 --> 00:11:40.828
AUDIENCE: [INAUDIBLE].

00:11:40.828 --> 00:11:41.977
